## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f996c-102">来自源事件 (trace 或 debug) 的所有事件数据都作为字符串写入到 ETW 子系统。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-102">All event data (trace or debug) from the source event is written to the ETW subsystem as a string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f996c-103">数据元素使用逗号进行分隔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-103">The data elements are delimited using a comma.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f996c-104">若要指定其他分隔符，请使用 <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProviderTraceListener.Delimiter%2A> 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-104">To specify a different delimiter, use the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProviderTraceListener.Delimiter%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f996c-105">添加侦听器，以将 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> 提供程序注册到 ETW 子系统。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-105">Adding the listener to <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> registers the provider with the ETW subsystem.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f996c-106">必须使用 Logman.exe 的可执行程序 (或类似) 创建 ETW 跟踪会话，以将事件写入日志文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-106">You must create an ETW trace session using the Logman.exe executable program (or something similar) to write the events to a log file.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f996c-107">你不需要清单来使用侦听器中的事件，因为事件数据是单个字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-107">You do not need a manifest to consume events from the listener because the event data is a single string.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f996c-108">调用 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法来写入事件时，将传递 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> 枚举值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-108">When you call the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=nameWithType> methods to write events, you pass a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f996c-109">枚举同时包含 level 和关键字值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-109">The enumeration contains both level and keyword values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f996c-110">当您从 ETW 会话启用跟踪侦听器提供程序时，您指定的级别值可以是与以下枚举值之一相关联的值 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-110">When you enable a trace listener provider from an ETW session, the level value that you specify can be the value associated with one of the following <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration values:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-111">严重 (值为 1) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-111">Critical (value is 1)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-112">错误 (值为 2) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-112">Error (value is 2)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-113">信息 (值为 8) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-113">Information (value is 8)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-114">详细 (值为 16) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-114">Verbose (value is 16)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-115">警告 (值为 4) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-115">Warning (value is 4)</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f996c-116">为会话指定的关键字值可以是与以下枚举值之一相关联的值 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-116">The keyword value that you specify for the session can be the value associated with one of the following <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration values:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-117">恢复 (值为 2048) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-117">Resume (value is 2,048)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-118">开始 (值为 256) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-118">Start (value is 256)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-119">Stop (值为 512) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-119">Stop (value is 512)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-120">挂起 (值为 1024) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-120">Suspend (value is 1,024)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f996c-121">传输 (值为 4096) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f996c-121">Transfer (value is 4,096)</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
private static Guid providerId = new Guid("{B3F0C8FC-E8A8-4868-8901-1465E8A2F41B}");  
  
    EventProviderTraceListener listener = new EventProviderTraceListener(providerId.ToString(), "Test Listener", "::");  
  
    // You should use the All default level and control the level using the  
    // ETW session; otherwise, you may not log all the events requested by the  
    // session.  
    TraceSource source = new TraceSource("MyProvider", SourceLevels.All);  
  
    source.Listeners.Add(listener);  
  
    source.TraceData(TraceEventType.Warning | TraceEventType.Start, 2, new object[] { "abc", "def", true, 123 });  
  
    source.TraceEvent(TraceEventType.Warning, 12, "Provider guid: {0}", new object[] { providerId });  
  
    source.TraceInformation("string {0}, bool {1}, int {2}, ushort {3}", new object[] { "abc", false, 123, (UInt32)5 });  
```
